description: Image Systems AB engages in the development, manufacturing, and trading of equipment for the processing, storage, and transmission of television, film, and media. The company is headquartered in Linkoping, Ostergotland and currently employs 90 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2013-08-19. First is TrackEye, which is primarily aimed towards the flight/military market. And the other package TEMA is aimed towards the automotive industry and is well adopted for use in other industrial applications.
name: Image Systems AB
